<chapeau style="-uslm-lc:I11" class="indent0">There are authorized to be appropriated to the Secretary to carry out the activities described in this subchapter—</chapeau><paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idc06098db-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s18655/1"><num value="1">(1)</num><content> $8,902,392,400 for fiscal year 2023;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idc06098dc-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s18655/2"><num value="2">(2)</num><content> $9,541,895,744 for fiscal year 2024;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idc06098dd-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s18655/3"><num value="3">(3)</num><content> $10,068,198,994 for fiscal year 2025;</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idc06098de-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s18655/4"><num value="4">(4)</num><content> $10,468,916,520 for fiscal year 2026; and</content>
</paragraph>
<paragraph style="-uslm-lc:I12" class="indent1" id="idc06098df-3a70-11f1-ae07-e4213316b5fa" identifier="/us/usc/t42/s18655/5"><num value="5">(5)</num><content> $10,831,342,317 for fiscal year 2027.</content>
</paragraph>
